  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK109">
<l>koṉṟaṉṉa viṉṉā ceyiṉu mavarceyta</l>
<l>voṉṟunaṉ ṟuḷḷak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if they do such wrong as to kill, think of one kindness</l>
<l>they have done—and it disappears.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
